    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>Our mission is to provide reliable, high-quality landscaping services that make our clients proud of their outdoor spaces. We aim to combine efficiency, craftsmanship, and a personal touch to ensure every yard reflects the personality and lifestyle of its owner.</p>

    <h2>Why Choose Us</h2>
    <p>At Greenside Crew, we believe your outdoors should be an extension of your home. With years of experience, attention to detail, and a commitment to excellence, we handle every task—from routine maintenance to complex landscaping projects—with professionalism and care. Your satisfaction is our top priority.</p>
